        <item>
            <title>任天堂博物馆 10 月京都开幕　可亲手制花牌 + 试玩巨型游戏机</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/20/nintendo-museum-open-in-october/hottopic/walk/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=nintendo-museum-open-in-october</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/20/nintendo-museum-open-in-october/hottopic/walk/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 11:00:05 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩乐好去处]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Nintendo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[任天堂]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1257325</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>任天堂位于京都宇治市的博物馆将于 2024 年 10 月 2 日正式开幕，成为游戏迷和历史爱好者的理想去处。这座博物馆将展出任天堂自创立以来的各种硬件和游戏产品，并设有互动体验区域，让参观者通过游戏和手作活动深入了解这家具有悠久历史的企业。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257344" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/uji_image-694x379.png" alt="" width="694" height="379" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/uji_image-694x379.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/uji_image.png 860w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲任天堂宇治工厂，图片来源：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">Nintendo</a></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257336" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image01-580x580.png" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image01-580x580.png 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image01.png 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image01-144x144.png 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">Nintendo</a></p><p>博物馆的展览将涵盖任天堂的早期作品如花牌，以及从 NES 到 Wii 等经典游戏机的发展历程。参观者更可以自费亲手制作花牌，体验传统游戏的魅力。除此之外，博物馆还设置了巨型的游戏控制器，让参观者以别样的方式重温经典游戏。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257338" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image03-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image03-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image03.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image03-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲参观者可亲手制作传统花牌，图片来源：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">Nintendo</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257337" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image02-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image02-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image02.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image02-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲博物馆内设有互动区域，图片来源：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">Nintendo</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257346" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image06-694x407.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="407" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image06-694x407.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image06.jpg 1160w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲设有特大游戏机让参观者体验经典游戏，图片来源：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">Nintendo</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257347" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image08-694x407.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="407" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image08-694x407.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image08.jpg 1160w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲巨型的游戏控制器，图片来源：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">Nintendo</a></p><p>博物馆内还有咖啡店，供应特制甜点和自选食材搭配的汉堡，并设有纪念品商店，提供限量版商品。值得一提的是，入馆证将采用参观者的 Mii 角色作为入场识别，并能保留在馆内的互动体验记录，让整个参观过程更加个性化。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257340" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image_slide01-694x453.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="453" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image_slide01-694x453.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image_slide01.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲博物馆内的咖啡店，图片来源：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">Nintendo</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257339" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image_slide02-694x453.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="453" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image_slide02-694x453.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image_slide02.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">Nintendo</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257341" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image_slide011-694x453.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="453" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image_slide011-694x453.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image_slide011.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">Nintendo</a></p><p>门票采用抽选制度，参观者需要提前通过任天堂博物馆的官方网站进行抽选，选中后缴纳门票费用即可获得参观资格。票价方面，成人票价为 3,300 日圆（约港币 175 元）、中学生和高中生为 2,200 日圆（约港币 116）元，小学生票价为 1,100 日圆（约港币 58 元），未满学龄的幼童可免费入场。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257343" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240820153157-694x295.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="295" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240820153157-694x295.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240820153157.jpg 1012w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲门票售价，图片来源：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">Nintendo</a></p><p>任天堂官方博物馆网站：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257335" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240820152649-694x517.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="517" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240820152649-694x517.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240820152649.jpg 1209w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">Nintendo</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257345" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240820153507-694x578.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="578" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240820153507-694x578.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240820153507.jpg 1081w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲博物馆位置，图片来源：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">Nintendo</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">Nintendo Museum</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/24/nonofficial-nintendo-kawaii/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">非官方「Nintendo Kawaii」面世　Wii 主机迷你化变锁匙扣大小</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/20/nintendo-museum-open-in-october/hottopic/walk/">任天堂博物馆 10 月京都开幕　可亲手制花牌 + 试玩巨型游戏机</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
